{"tid":177322,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"買貓一問","createTime":"2017-03-28T18:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T02:22:18.000Z","uid":61359,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a757a66bdc8f924fa4827c19cef6582012d6e61","tid":177322,"uid":61359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T18:43:27.000Z","msg":"究竟有冇地方可以買唐貓,上網睇全部都係名種貓(除左美短算靚之外其他都唔鍾意),最鍾意係虎紋唐貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去過spca領養2次都唔成功,又聽到佢地d職員hold貓俾熟人,未上網就hold左一日就無埋,仲講大話呃我d貓有病唔領養得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後又搵過貓義工,但係俾佢張form嚇到我鳩都縮,借大耳窿都唔洗咁詳細,仲要填完唔一定有得領養,又唔知佢乜頭乜路<br />\n<br />\n搞左咁耐最尾覺得不如買好過,有無好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f368d2c55105a4f1296252e3f60ca4fa2499d6fa","tid":177322,"uid":12839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T18:45:44.000Z","msg":"係連登講買貓=比人binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411222349d8a1674c0a7c4f2633b20db9d035dd7","tid":177322,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T18:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係連登講買貓=比人binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咩？屌緊啲濕鳩義工好耐啦"},{"pid":"f31a79aec5bd603e28d963ecd3ab31282037b2a6","tid":177322,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T20:23:34.000Z","msg":"買你老母，咁多貓可以領養唔去領<br />\n係要用錢買，啲貓點黎又唔撚理<br />\n就係樓主呢啲仆街先搞到商人唔理啲貓嘅感受走去配種<br />\n然後啲冚家產以為自己俾咗錢大撚哂<br />\n養幾日唔happy就棄貓<br />\n成個生態圈搞到亂哂<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母買貓果啲全撚部仆街死"},{"pid":"3f0be47e47313e499078d7f09f76b539b605c730","tid":177322,"uid":76879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T20:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買你老母，咁多貓可以領養唔去領<br />\n係要用錢買，啲貓點黎又唔撚理<br />\n就係樓主呢啲仆